                    <item>
              <title>How Simplicity Gets Results with eLearning</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/9211</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/9211</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>Imagine a scenario where you have an imminently upcoming deadline for a big assignment and have swathes of materials to get through. You&rsquo;re not only going to struggle to absorb or retain the information, but you&rsquo;re always going to approach with a sense of dread at the large task at hand.</p>
<p>This is where simple, effective learning can prove to be a saviour; cut away the excess fat and leave yourself with the straightforward numbers and facts. If you&rsquo;re searching for eLearning for your workforce, this is something important to keep in mind.</p>
<p>As a learning method, eLearning has seen a steady rise to become one of the best ways to garner new knowledge and get to grips with new skills over the past decade. The levels of interactivity can&rsquo;t be matched by a simple classroom tuition and it&rsquo;s proven to be a much more cost and time-effective measure.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.scormexplained.com/2015/05/how-simplicity-gets-results-with-elearning/"><strong>READ MORE</strong></a></p>]]></description>
          <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2015 13:52:53 +0000</pubDate>
