              <description><![CDATA[<p>Hello!</p>
<p>My name is Lu&iacute;s Salema. I&rsquo;m from Portugal.</p>
<p>I&rsquo;m a teacher of Portuguese language and literature, latin and greek, at secondary school.</p>
<p>I worked at the University of the Algarve and I&rsquo;m a on line tutor at Universidade Aberta (Portuguese Open University).</p>
<p>I have a Master in Sciences of Speech and Hearing. My dissertation was in the intersection field of dialectology, experimental phonetics and computer language processing.</p>
<p>I have a post graduate course in Information Management and School Libraries.</p>
<p>Now, I&rsquo;m a PhD student at Universidade Aberta (Distance Education and E-learning).</p>
<p>As a researcher, my interests are language learning, online language learning and linguistics.</p>
<p>I&rsquo;m very curious about history, classical studies and about different countries and cultures.</p>
<p>I like to travel and to learn more. I think this new online experience will be great. I will have the opportunity to learn more about learning design and about technology, with people from different countries and with different approaches to these areas.</p>
