                    <item>
              <title>Apps for education</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/5271</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/5271</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>An ongoing list of links to apps for educational/classroom use:</p>
<p><a href="http://www.appsineducation.com/">Apps in Education</a> (useful blog site dedicated to the subject)</p>
<p><a href="http://www.ipadappspro.com/m/education-ipad-apps-1.html">iPadAppsPro</a> (list of up to 30 apps)</p>
<p><a href="http://reacheverychild.com/feature/apps.html">Horace Mann</a> (list of Apple and Android apps)</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.simplek12.com/education/5-free-iphone-apps-for-the-classroom/">Five free iPhone apps for the classroom</a> (WordPress, iFlashCards, etc.)</p>
<p><a href="http://sites.google.com/site/technologyenhancedlearning/ipod-touch-iphone-resources">Various iPod Touch and iPhone resources</a> (Evernote, etc.)</p>
